gosian=E2=80=99s stable, said in her lecture at the Menil Collection a year=
 ago, =E2=80=9Cthere was a challenge of sorts going on between Twombly and =
Larry Gagosian.=E2=80=9D As Saville described it, this game of one-upsmansh=
