le-lot auction held at the Mercedes-Benz Museum in Stuttgart. One of only f=
our versions of the Mercedes W 196 R with a streamlined chassis,
this car was originally donated by the automaker to the Indianapolis Motor =
Speedway Museum, which is now selling it to benefit its collection and rest=
oration efforts. Three years ago, Mercedes sold a related car, the gull-win=
