00;">according</a> to Artnet, are all new=E2=80=94made between late last ye=
ar and as recently as last month.<br/><br/>While the themes and images are =
classic Condo, the 20 large-scale works were all made with pastels, which a=
llowed the artist to produce them more quickly. On Friday, as I toured the =
shows=E2=80=94both of which are quite good, especially the Hauser show in S=
